     * @fires Phaser.Cameras.Scene2D.Events#FADE_OUT_START
     * @since 3.5.0
     *
     * @param {boolean} [direction=true] - The direction of the fade. `true` = fade out (transparent to color), `false` = fade in (color to transparent)
